  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation of mdev-like-a-boss</title>

    <para>Change the path for the helper scripts:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="configure">sed 's|opt/mdev/helpers|sbin|' -i mdev.conf</userinput></screen>

    <para>Install the package:</para>

<screen><userinput remap="install">install -v -m 644 mdev.conf /etc/</userinput></screen>
install -v -m 755 helpers/catch-all /sbin/
install -v -m 755 helpers/proc-bus-usb /sbin/
install -v -m 755 helpers/settle-nics /sbin/
install -v -m 755 helpers/storage-device /sbin/</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

